criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age ≥50;

          -  Can attend a 2-hour session (though both PHARM and PEER entail 60 minutes of
             intervention, an additional hour is needed to allow for informed consent and data
             collection);

          -  Speak and read English at ≥4th grade level as determined by a brief reading passage;

          -  Cognitively intact as evidenced by an Abbreviated Mental Status Test score ≥7.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Failure to meet inclusion criteria

          -  Failure to give informed consent to participate in the study
